ideo/7565587290043469078', description='Zum benutzen oder verschenken Mega!! #gaming #stuhl ', author='reapez'), VideoModel(video_id='7496992503585901870', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@uyibear/video/7496992503585901870', description='this chair is like a cloud ☁️ @Dowinx @Dowinx EU @Dowinx_official #whitepc #whitesetup #setupinspo #dowinx #dowinxgamingchair #dowinxchair #chair #officechair #TechTok #tiktoklearningcampaign #cozysetup #cozygaming #cozy #setupideas #trending', author='uyibear'), VideoModel(video_id='7577710085607034134', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@kochfreaks/video/7577710085607034134', description='Symino Gaming Stuhl  #symino #gaming #gamingstuhl #tiktokshop #blackfriday ', author='kochfreaks'), VideoModel(video_id='7553027472401485078', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@shopfinds2024/video/7553027472401485078', description='Replying to @Iz the more I see this getting used, the more convinced I am of its value - it’s so comfortable and he loves it! #gamingchair #gamingchairs #gamers #tiktokmademebuyit ', author='shopfinds2024'), VideoModel(video_id='7498734215622577430', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@goodwinchris/video/7498734215622577430', description='Mach nicht den Selben fehler wie ich . Jetzt vom Hersteller direkt.  #interessant #kurz #fürdich #fd #tiktokshop #Shop #gamingstuhl ', author='goodwinchris'), VideoModel(video_id='7458899565475876127', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@oranotrita/video/7458899565475876127', description='Finally a chair that is comfy, cute, supported and functional.👏🏼 @Dowinx #gamingchair #officechair #gamingsetup #chair ', author='oranotrita'), VideoModel(video_id='7541096720558492950', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@slintix/video/7541096720558492950', description='Level up your Setup 🎮✨ Mit dem SYMINO Gaming-Stuhl – ergonomisch, bequem & voll verstellbar für stundenlangen Komfort. 🪑🔥 #dealsfürdich #gamingstuhl #gaming #büro #symino ', author='slintix'), VideoModel(video_id='7525862594960166166', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@lost