tps://www.tiktok.com/@techtesseract/video/7539958245755063566', description="They said the perfect gaming chair dosent exist… and hbada said bet 🍺😂👌  I’ve been using the Hbada X7 for over a month now, and it’s officially my favorite chair of the year 😍😍😍...and that’s saying something because I’ve reviewed a lot of chairs!  The massage is sooo strong… Sometimes, I have to turn it off because it digs into your back 😌 in the best way possible. The heated seat makes gaming under a blanket even cozier, and the built in fans? You literally feel the seat cool down the second you turn them on.  If you’re looking for the ultimate gaming chair for your setup, this one’s definitely Nay Nay approved! 10/10 would highly recommend 👌 👏 😍  Might seem a little overkill, but it's definitely a gamers dream chair👌. Link’s in my bio if you want to check it out!  #ergonomicchair #gamingsetups #techtok  #gamingchair #hbada ", author='techtesseract'), VideoModel(video_id='7449161068825300257', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@.hypey/video/7449161068825300257', description='I bought the best chair with @SIHOO Office #officechair #gamingchair #sihoo #sihooc300 #Hypey ', author='.hypey'), VideoModel(video_id='7406733378143259946', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@techtesseract/video/7406733378143259946', description="Is this not the perfect chair for gaming? 😍 I've never had a chair with a built-in Footrest, and now that I have I've realized how big of a difference it really makes! You best believe I'll be in my living room all the time now lounging and gaming! At some point I'd like to build a desk that mounts over the arms so it's a portable moving workstation! This chair is Definitely NayNay approved and I would highly recommend! The HBADA E3 Chair is also 30% off on amazon right now too, so its the perfect time to pick it up, Link in Bio @Hbada Ergonomic Office Chair  #pcgamingsetup #gamingroom #fyp #pcsetup #techtok #setupinspiration #gamingsetup #HBADA #E3 #HbadaE3ErgonomicOfficeChair #blendedgtalks #verydemure #verymindful ", author='techtesseract'), VideoModel(video_id='7327057276781579563', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@paulramjohnfinds/video/7327057276781579563', description='HUGE 🚨42% off 🚨 get it now while supplies last.  My apologies I’m unable to put a link in my bio being that I don’t have 1000 followers yet. However you can search on amazon for “GTPLAYER Gaming Chair, Computer Chair ” or you can get a direct link in my bio on my instagram page with the same username as this one. Thanks for following and helping me grow. #GamingChair #Amazon #gamingchairamazon ', author='paulramjohnfinds'), VideoModel(video_id='7562291181456002326', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@katjadaniel_/video/7562291181456002326', description='Gemütlich Chillig dieser Gamingstuhl 😍 auch perfekt für das Büro, Schreibtisch, Nageltisch uvm. 💁🏼\u200d♀️ Jetzt im TikTok Shop bestellen 🛒🛍️ #katjatestet #gaming #zocken #gamingstuhl #zocker ', author='katjadaniel_'), VideoModel(video_id='7423129703378193695', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@sandravlogz/video/7423129703378193695', description='pink gaming chair unboxing🩰🩷 #fypシ #gamingchair #pink #gaming #gamergirl #unboxing #tiktokshopfinds ', author='sandravlogz'), VideoModel(video_id='7435849288267173162', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@winwithnick/video/7435849288267173162', description='Incredible Gaming Chair. perfect Christmas gift. #gaming #gamer  #gamingchair #christmas #tiktokshopblackfriday #tiktokshopcybermonday #gift ', author='winwithnick'), VideoModel(video_id='7523436026803653910', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@symino_de/video/7523436026803653910', description='De beste stoel❤️❤️❤️#gaming #symino #gamingchair #geweldige #tiktoklive #livehighlights ', author='symino_de'), VideoModel(video_id='7525514880309267734', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@lost.express24.7/video/7525514880309267734', description='Perfekt fürs Zocken und maximal bequem ! Link in der Video beschreibung oder schau auf meinen Kanal dort findest du mehr 🫵🏽 #gaming #stuhl #gamingstuhl #gamingsetup #tiktokshop #fyp #fürdich #voiceeffects #videoviral #viralvideos #comment #views #symino ', author='lost.express24.7'), VideoModel(video_id='7565530236897496322', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@gold..junge/video/7565530236897496322', description='Neuer Gaming Stuhl 🤩 #stuhl #gaming #sitzen #büro #gamingsetup ', author='gold..junge'), VideoModel(video_id='7579469708353735958', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@symino_gm/video/7579469708353735958', description='De best verkochte stoel! Welkom om een bestelling te plaatsen❤️\u200d🔥#tiktoklive #gamingchair #symino #sofa #fyp ', author='symino_gm'), VideoModel(video_id='7575590290615012630', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@jyzzh18/video/7575590290615012630', description='I bought the best chair with @SIHOO Office #officechair#fyp#tiktokshop #gamingchair #sihoo #sihooc300 #Hypey', author='jyzzh18'), VideoModel(video_id='7552471207489178902', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@giigkhgkhg/video/7552471207489178902', description='🎮 Ultimativer Gaming-Thron: Der Stuhl für echte Zocker! 🖤🔥 #GamingStuhl #ZockerLife #GamerRoom #BattleStation #tiktokshop ', author='giigkhgkhg'), VideoModel(video_id='7518611328366284054', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@symino_de/video/7518611328366284054', description='The best chair ❤️❤️❤️#gaming #symino #gamingchair ', author='symino_de'), VideoModel(video_id='7507951798708210966', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@symino_de/video/7507951798708210966', description='Button Price in live!! #symino #gamingchair #tiktoklive ', author='symino_de')]}
