talks #verydemure #verymindful ", author='techtesseract'), VideoModel(video_id='7327057276781579563', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@paulramjohnfinds/video/7327057276781579563', description='HUGE 🚨42% off 🚨 get it now while supplies last.  My apologies I’m unable to put a link in my bio being that I don’t have 1000 followers yet. However you can search on amazon for “GTPLAYER Gaming Chair, Computer Chair ” or you can get a direct link in my bio on my instagram page with the same username as this one. Thanks for following and helping me grow. #GamingChair #Amazon #gamingchairamazon ', author='paulramjohnfinds'), VideoModel(video_id='7562291181456002326', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@katjadaniel_/video/7562291181456002326', description='Gemütlich Chillig dieser Gamingstuhl 😍 auch perfekt für das Büro, Schreibtisch, Nageltisch uvm. 💁🏼\u200d♀️ Jetzt im TikTok Shop bestellen 🛒🛍️ #katjatestet #gaming #zocken #gamingstuhl #zocker ', author='katjadaniel_'), VideoModel(video_id='7423129703378193695', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@sandravlogz/video/7423129703378193695', description='pink gaming chair unboxing🩰🩷 #fypシ #gamingchair #pink #gaming #gamergirl #unboxing #tiktokshopfinds ', author='sandravlogz'), VideoModel(video_id='7435849288267173162', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@winwithnick/video/7435849288267173162', description='Incredible Gaming Chair. perfect Christmas gift. #gaming #gamer  #gamingchair #christmas #tiktokshopblackfriday #tiktokshopcybermonday #gift ', author='winwithnick'), VideoModel(video_id='7523436026803653910', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@symino_de/video/7523436026803653910', description='De beste stoel❤️❤️❤️#gaming #symino #gamingchair #geweldige #tiktoklive #livehighlights ', author='symino_de'), VideoModel(video_id='7525514880309267734', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@lost.express24.7/video/7525514880309267734', description='Perfekt fürs Zocken und maximal bequem ! Link in der Video beschreibung oder schau auf meinen Kanal dort findest du mehr 🫵🏽 #gamin